      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 189.32,
      "time_str": "03:09.320",
      "text": "那饱满的稻穗 幸福了这个季节",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 196.44,
      "time_str": "03:16.440",
      "text": "而你的脸颊像田里熟透的番茄",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 202.801,
      "time_str": "03:22.801",
      "text": "你突然对我说 七里香的名字很美",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 209.149,
      "time_str": "03:29.149",
      "text": "我此刻却只想亲吻你倔强的嘴",
      "translation": null
